{"tid":2063350,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[批袁批孔] 質疑袁國勇新冠研究 吳秋北炮轟：「美國強有力的外援！」","createTime":"2020-06-14T01:48:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-14T06:17:28.000Z","uid":224066,"like":149,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":99,"replies":[{"pid":"83c030fbe75f2f2b38bd27e3f774d15c5b65812b","tid":2063350,"uid":224066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T01:48:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media-proc.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2020/06/20200613_CR_%E5%90%B3%E7%A7%8B%E5%8C%971_FB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia-proc.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2020%2F06%2F20200613_CR_%25E5%2590%25B3%25E7%25A7%258B%25E5%258C%25971_FB.jpg&h=7919a50e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n吳又揶揄袁國勇將共產黨「神化」了<br />\n<br />\n港大微生物學系講座教授袁國勇及其團隊近日發表就新冠肺炎抗體進行研究，發現從452名湖北返港的無症狀香港居民中，近4％人具有抗體。團隊以此推算湖北5,900萬人口當中，可能有高達220萬人曾受感染。工聯會會長吳秋北昨日則發文質疑相關研究，又指「袁科學家是美國強有力的外援」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://media-proc.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2020/06/20200613_CR_%E5%90%B3%E7%A7%8B%E5%8C%972.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia-proc.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2020%2F06%2F20200613_CR_%25E5%2590%25B3%25E7%25A7%258B%25E5%258C%25972.jpg&h=ec0fcb6f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n吳秋北昨日發文批評，袁國勇以「不懂政治」包裝政治主導科學、再以「科學」包裝「不懂政治」的政治。他又質疑相關研究的結果，並指「用400多樣本就能推算220萬人受感染，以此計算，14億中國人口，不是有5.3千萬受感染？！這麼驚人的數字，內地還能這麼平靜，陸續復工，那當真不是將共產黨妖魔化，而是神化了！」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n他又指，「袁科學家是美國強有力的外援」，並指對方又一次「適時」的為美國打擊中國落力配合。他又質疑，袁國勇「放著武漢1億核酸檢測數據不用，偏偏用這400多樣本，其中奧妙何在？就像放著中國14億公民的民意忽略不計，只聽零星幾個港獨份子大聲叫囂，那又代表得了甚麼？！科學、民意全部政治化，實際就是訛詐！」"},{"pid":"43bac49bf0ebbdeae7fa0757477f742bcb87ad52","tid":2063350,"uid":37389,"like":152,"dislike":2,"score":150,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T01:51:06.000Z","msg":"唔知講咩好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 全世界都通用嘅研究推論方法都可以屈落美國度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bbef4e518e0a015cbd7384fbcd057346e1ea267","tid":2063350,"uid":326287,"like":98,"dislike":2,"score":96,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T01:51:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />加速，不學無術批鬥醫學權威<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"299e9657c16de1ba0ccada5ff2a97a896c216ec2","tid":2063350,"uid":59929,"like":37,"dislike":0,"score":37,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T01:52:28.000Z","msg":"佢去做醫學顧問得啦"},{"pid":"7d487d752937b65f6a66344c590a9997a5c4e050","tid":2063350,"uid":130105,"like":39,"dislike":1,"score":38,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T01:53:58.000Z","msg":"袁國勇現在已變錢學森第二都人批鬥<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e8692b75c68687a9bdf295a9b86bfa49131e3ad","tid":2063350,"uid":22624,"like":61,"dislike":2,"score":59,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T01:58:12.000Z","msg":"吳秋北：14億中國人口，不是有5.3千萬受感染？"},{"pid":"2e1a5ca44f101d9c5cd3c9b2d4a1c318d1088a74","tid":2063350,"uid":172627,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"43bac49bf0ebbdeae7fa0757477f742bcb87ad52","tid":2063350,"uid":37389,"like":152,"dislike":2,"score":150,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T01:51:06.000Z","msg":"唔知講咩好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 全世界都通用嘅研究推論方法都可以屈落美國度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T01:58:37.000Z","msg":"美國=科學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a3c4c4d432f014feb3e8085b3b739d277a7ee43","tid":2063350,"uid":84128,"like":48,"dislike":1,"score":47,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T01:59:23.000Z","msg":"袁：咁我咪收回返囉<br />\n我唔識政治架喇"},{"pid":"e29b8b9018a43d670d71c9ebd91a8e50828e33a5","tid":206335