nt-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Ignorance creates chaos</span></span>"},{"pid":"a3bf33523e1121865540bf668054639e47311279","tid":2063350,"uid":57828,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"83c030fbe75f2f2b38bd27e3f774d15c5b65812b","tid":2063350,"uid":224066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T01:48:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media-proc.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2020/06/20200613_CR_%E5%90%B3%E7%A7%8B%E5%8C%971_FB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia-proc.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2020%2F06%2F20200613_CR_%25E5%2590%25B3%25E7%25A7%258B%25E5%258C%25971_FB.jpg&h=7919a50e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n吳又揶揄袁國勇將共產黨「神化」了<br />\n<br />\n港大微生物學系講座教授袁國勇及其團隊近日發表就新冠肺炎抗體進行研究，發現從452名湖北返港的無症狀香港居民中，近4％人具有抗體。團隊以此推算湖北5,900萬人口當中，可能有高達220萬人曾受感染。工聯會會長吳秋北昨日則發文質疑相關研究，又指「袁科學家是美國強有力的外援」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://media-proc.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2020/06/20200613_CR_%E5%90%B3%E7%A7%8B%E5%8C%972.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia-proc.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2020%2F06%2F20200613_CR_%25E5%2590%25B3%25E7%25A7%258B%25E5%258C%25972.jpg&h=ec0fcb6f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n吳秋北昨日發文批評，袁國勇以「不懂政治」包裝政治主導科學、再以「科學」包裝「不懂政治」的政治。他又質疑相關研究的結果，並指「用400多樣本就能推算220萬人受感染，以此計算，14億中國人口，不是有5.3千萬受感染？！這麼驚人的數字，內地還能這麼平靜，陸續復工，那當真不是將共產黨妖魔化，而是神化了！」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n他又指，「袁科學家是美國強有力的外援」，並指對方又一次「適時」的為美國打擊中國落力配合。他又質疑，袁國勇「放著武漢1億核酸檢測數據不用，偏偏用這400多樣本，其中奧妙何在？就像放著中國14億公民的民意忽略不計，只聽零星幾個港獨份子大聲叫囂，那又代表得了甚麼？！科學、民意全部政治化，實際就是訛詐！」"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T02:35:47.000Z","msg":"聽過呢隻共狗講野 真係只有狗主人先明佢講咩"},{"pid":"0d66ae3f1dae765ad0d9383931d98e5fba679f73","tid":2063350,"uid":199771,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T02:37:51.000Z","msg":"袁國勇之前話香港有1.4M人感染<br />\n佢好似估緊係美國而唔係香港"},{"pid":"6108e375f68e7a976defc60336cc30cda2082ed7","tid":2063350,"uid":54344,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T02:38:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>科學、民意全部政治化</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52e4061cb73e24917b2cf8f48533a73cdc26cf1c","tid":2063350,"uid":129030,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1bbef4e518e0a015cbd7384fbcd057346e1ea267","tid":2063350,"uid":326287,"like":98,"dislike":2,"score":96,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T01:51:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />加速，不學無術批鬥醫學權威<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T02:40:04.000Z","msg":"人地呢啲頂級人才去到邊都搶住收<br />\n係香港就做仆街野想迫人走"},{"pid":"971c9573cd03993422101bc2646bebd25007dfc1","tid":2063350,"uid":205927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T02:40:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebf4500256228030b4b57b79486e68ba33fb00c5","tid":2063350,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T02:40:54.000Z","msg":"文革2.0"},{"pid":"39241dd9fcf47f79be16dead680ca7256bb36892","tid":2063350,"uid":184756,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T02:41:19.000Z","msg":"1億核酸樣本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你無誠信講幾多樣本都係唔可信"},{"pid":"8c1dc952464fc6df4b951c222ec71eb8de6dbb79","tid":2063350,"uid":294501,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T02:41:35.000Z","msg":"屌，真係好憎呢啲人，<br />\n自己唔係專家，又咩都唔識，仲要煞其事衝出黎柒，為佢的中國